{"tid":40854,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【意國獸醫狩獵摔山谷亡　網民留言：報應！】","createTime":"2016-12-15T12:51:15.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-16T05:30:11.000Z","uid":22675,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"57392dea7d52f5110ab2eeb99336d0de55bc6556","tid":40854,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T12:51:15.000Z","msg":"興趣為獵殺野生動物的意大利獸醫Luciano Ponzetto，曾於網上張貼親自獵殺的大型動物合照，惹來炮轟。當時他表示自己一點都沒有做錯，狩獵是合法的行為，明言會繼續打獵直到不能夠打獵為止。<br />\n<br />\n近日報道指他打獵時失足跌落山谷慘死。據《太陽報》報道，Luciano近日在意大利北部狩獵鳥類時，不慎失足摔落約30米深的山谷，同行友人見狀連忙報警尋救援，送院前已無生命跡象，送院後傷重不治。當地警方指，事發原因為失足墜崖。<br />\n<br />\n全文︰<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/12-15-2016/34564\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F12-15-2016%2F34564&d=FGuILpbWDgP7IrF7AAea7gT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=d2f4df8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/12-15-2016/34564</a>"},{"pid":"83dd638c8f745a091721582456788e4b4f128e03","tid":40854,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T12:56:13.000Z","msg":"會唔會係俾人推落山"},{"pid":"30248679a3430b7d622d13521db6e70132f62029","tid":40854,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T13:30:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a07c2fe7df6a15605e4e2eb33609674d691a05a","tid":40854,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T00:52:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53044b9ee72d4736e20f2c27cd91c904eca8766d","tid":40854,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T01:45:44.000Z","msg":"instant justice <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0adf82ea9018987f549ae80d15fb3f7cfb694cd","tid":40854,"uid":53602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl